1:09:46.888 --> 1:09:50.424
<i>A sleepover?</i>
<i>Are they with you?</i>
<i>Are your friends with you?</i>

1:09:51.258 --> 1:09:52.694
-Yeah.
<i>-They're with her.</i>

1:09:52.727 --> 1:09:54.428
<i>They want to have</i>
<i>a sleepover or something.</i>

1:09:54.461 --> 1:09:56.664
<i>- They're there.</i>
<i>- Thank God.</i>

1:09:56.698 --> 1:10:00.400
- Um, Mom...
<i>- Honey, yes. What is it?</i>

1:10:04.706 --> 1:10:05.873
He was here.

1:10:20.722 --> 1:10:21.756
Hey.

1:10:23.725 --> 1:10:24.759
Hey.

1:10:38.539 --> 1:10:39.574
D--

1:10:42.877 --> 1:10:44.712
How-- How do you feel?

1:10:46.581 --> 1:10:47.615
Just that?

1:10:51.753 --> 1:10:54.756
Do you wanna...
Why didn't you
tell me the truth?

1:11:03.396 --> 1:11:05.298
That's fair. Um...

1:11:09.871 --> 1:11:12.540
I really, um...

1:11:14.575 --> 1:11:16.343
I tried.

1:11:16.376 --> 1:11:19.814
I did.
You really should have
told me the truth.

1:11:21.983 --> 1:11:23.283
I tried.

1:11:26.087 --> 1:11:30.057
If I--
If I had told you,
Daisy, then...

1:11:32.693 --> 1:11:33.795
then it would all...

1:11:36.864 --> 1:11:38.498
then it-- then it's real.

1:11:41.969 --> 1:11:44.437
And I... ...you know...

1:11:46.941 --> 1:11:50.645
I wasn't ready for that.

1:11:52.580 --> 1:11:54.048
But you're-- you're right.

1:11:55.049 --> 1:11:58.886
Was it because of me?
Was it my fault?

1:11:59.821 --> 1:12:00.855
No.

1:12:01.856 --> 1:12:02.990
Good God.

1:12:05.760 --> 1:12:06.794
No.

1:12:13.167 --> 1:12:14.869
Why would you say that?

1:12:15.770 --> 1:12:17.404
He didn't want us.

1:12:22.143 --> 1:12:23.376
I do.

1:12:25.012 --> 1:12:27.949
I want us too.
- You do? Good.

1:12:27.982 --> 1:12:29.851
'Cause that's what you got.

1:12:39.927 --> 1:12:41.361
Oh, man.

1:12:42.495 --> 1:12:43.764
You're a good one.

1:12:46.167 --> 1:12:49.537
You're a good one too.
Thanks.

1:12:55.843 --> 1:12:57.144
Hi.

1:13:14.929 --> 1:13:17.198
Hey, can I--
Let me-- Let me help you.

1:13:17.231 --> 1:13:18.966
- No. No. No.
- No worries.

1:13:20.635 --> 1:13:24.437
Man, I feel like, you know,
you reach a certain age,

1:13:24.471 --> 1:13:28.776
and suddenly you sort of
forget to make new friends.

1:13:28.809 --> 1:13:31.444
- You know what I mean?
- Yes.

1:13:31.478 --> 1:13:34.882
It can happen at any age.
Thank you. Thank you.

1:13:34.916 --> 1:13:39.020
We were
just like them once, right?
I mean, do you remember that?

1:13:39.053 --> 1:13:40.721
- Don't know.
- God, I do.

1:13:40.755 --> 1:13:43.524
I-I like to think so.
But I don't really remember.

1:13:43.557 --> 1:13:44.592
Man.

1:13:56.904 --> 1:13:57.939
You guys.

1:16:00.795 --> 1:16:02.163
<i>In the fall,</i>

1:16:03.264 --> 1:16:05.299
<i>I guess some things die</i>

1:16:06.734 --> 1:16:08.936
<i>to leave room for new things.</i>

1:16:11.005 --> 1:16:14.175
<i>I don't know if that's</i>
<i>a good thing or a bad thing.</i>

1:16:15.376 --> 1:16:16.844
<i>It's just a thing.</i>

1:16:17.878 --> 1:16:19.346
<i>It's just the way it is.</i>

1:16:33.727 --> 1:16:35.329
Can we all keep hanging out?

1:17:10.331 --> 1:17:11.732
He's gone.

1:17:15.703 --> 1:17:16.837
Our tree.

1:17:35.756 --> 1:17:38.058
Maybe he was never really here.

1:19:42.483 --> 1:19:44.351
I don't want
this weekend to end.

1:19:45.853 --> 1:19:47.354
I don't want us to end.

1:19:49.256 --> 1:19:50.991
I love you guys.

1:19:51.025 --> 1:19:54.295
I love that I get to be alive
when you're all alive.

1:20:00.067 --> 1:20:04.171
Let's never not be friends.

1:20:05.339 --> 1:20:06.373
Okay?
